    <title type="html"><![CDATA[An awesome generator for Codeigniter]]></title>
    <link href="http://ederribeiro.github.io/an-awesome-generator-for-codeigniter/"/>
    <updated>2015-02-28T16:34:45-03:00</updated>
    <id>http://ederribeiro.github.io/an-awesome-generator-for-codeigniter</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Hey! I&rsquo;ll show you now a way to save your time when you need to install a copy of the powerful <a href="http://www.codeigniter.com/">CodeIgniter</a> php framework.</p>

<blockquote><p><strong>all we need to do is&hellip;</strong></p>

<ul>
<li>Install <a href="http://yeoman.io/">Yeoman</a></li>
<li>Install the <a href="https://github.com/ederribeiro/generator-apu-codeigniter">generator</a></li>
<li>Initiate the generator</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>

<p>and is simpler than it looks, see:</p>

<h4>To install Yeoman:</h4>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ npm install -g yo</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h4>To install generator from npm, run:</h4>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ npm install -g generator-apu-codeigniter</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h4>Finally, initiate the generator:</h4>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ yo apu-codeigniter</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>after that your generator is ready.</p>

<hr />

<h2>Some things can be useful</h2>

<h4>Install <a href="http://gruntjs.com/">Grunt</a></h4>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ npm install -g grunt-cli</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h4>Install <a href="http://bower.io/">Bower</a></h4>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ npm install -g bower</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h4>Install <a href="https://getcomposer.org/">Composer</a></h4>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ curl -sS https://getcomposer.org/installer | php
</span><span class='line'>$ mv composer.phar /usr/local/bin/composer</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h4>Install dependencies</h4>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ npm install
</span><span class='line'>$ bower install
</span><span class='line'>$ composer update</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h4>Build</h4>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ grunt build</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h4>Set permissions (maybe you need set permission 777 to application/cache folder)</h4>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ chmod 777 application/cache</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>and It&rsquo;s all folks!</p>

<hr />

<p>I hope help you with these steps, to have a powerful application as quickly as possible.</p>

<p>Feel free to find me and take any questions. Please give your feedback, comment and share it.</p>

<p>Thanks a lot!!</p>
